gov.nasa.gsfc.hessi.jidl.prep.server.Parameter
Class PrepParameterSet

java.lang.Object
  gov.nasa.gsfc.hessi.jidl.prep.server.Parameter.PrepParameterSet

public class PrepParameterSet
extends java.lang.Object

This class is being sent from the client to the server and contains a set of PrepParameter that will be used by the IDL instrument preprocessing routines.

Since:
Revision 19
Author:
Laszlo Istvan Etesi
